1430
00:59:11,200 --> 00:59:11,840
Enda and I

1431
00:59:11,840 --> 00:59:14,280
can go from two individuals

1432
00:59:14,280 --> 00:59:15,400
to becoming

1433
00:59:15,400 --> 00:59:17,200
something better together.

1434
00:59:22,080 --> 00:59:24,000
Honestly, I do feel a little sad.

1435
00:59:24,800 --> 00:59:27,400
Thinking about the possibility that we might

1436
00:59:27,400 --> 00:59:28,440
not see each other,

1437
00:59:28,600 --> 00:59:30,720
and can only stay in touch by phone,

1438
00:59:32,920 --> 00:59:34,280
it hurts.

1439
00:59:36,520 --> 00:59:37,800
After leaving Balance Island,

1440
00:59:37,800 --> 00:59:40,040
we might really not be able

1441
00:59:40,040 --> 00:59:41,280
to be like we are here,

1442
00:59:41,280 --> 00:59:42,400
seeing each other every day,

1443
00:59:42,400 --> 00:59:44,280
talking every day,

1444
00:59:44,280 --> 00:59:47,400
and doing meaningful things together.

1445
00:59:54,200 --> 00:59:56,240
Why do I suddenly feel so nervous here?

1446
00:59:57,800 --> 00:59:59,080
What are you nervous about?

1447
00:59:59,800 --> 01:00:00,760
Nervous.

1448
01:00:00,760 --> 01:00:01,720
How could I not be?

1449
01:00:13,040 --> 01:00:14,400
So, Yang...

1450
01:00:28,340 --> 01:00:45,300
("Live and Love" Release Schedule)

1451
01:00:45,300 --> 01:00:48,380
(Preview)

1452
01:00:48,400 --> 01:00:49,680
Thanks for being here.

1453
01:00:49,680 --> 01:00:51,880
You made me feel
the desire for love again.

1454
01:00:52,160 --> 01:00:53,440
Call me often.

1455
01:00:53,440 --> 01:00:54,200
Stay in touch.

1456
01:00:54,200 --> 01:00:55,040
Don't forget me.

1457
01:00:55,400 --> 01:00:56,760
In the days to come,

1458
01:00:56,880 --> 01:00:59,240
I'll protect you like a seashell.

1459
01:00:59,360 --> 01:01:00,600
If you're willing,

1460
01:01:00,600 --> 01:01:02,080
light up this sparkler

1461
01:01:02,080 --> 01:01:03,080
and tell me

1462
01:01:03,080 --> 01:01:03,800
that you're in.

1463
01:01:04,680 --> 01:01:05,760
Lighting this sparkler

1464
01:01:05,760 --> 01:01:07,360
means we're making it official.

1465
01:01:09,600 --> 01:01:11,520
They say love reflects hardships.

1466
01:01:11,880 --> 01:01:14,080
I believe love conquers them too.

1467
01:01:19,160 --> 01:01:19,920
Yang!

1468
01:01:21,840 --> 01:01:23,640
Love watching this.

1469
01:01:24,880 --> 01:01:25,920
(Pursue love on Balance Island)
Now,

1470
01:01:25,920 --> 01:01:27,320
(Every Wed. at 12 pm)
I'm off to get Yan

1471
01:01:27,320 --> 01:01:28,000
a keepsake.

1472
01:01:28,320 --> 01:01:30,680
I can't wait to see what he's prepared.

1473
01:01:30,680 --> 01:01:32,200
Maybe something with seashells?

1474
01:01:32,200 --> 01:01:33,520
Every time he opens this notebook,

1475
01:01:33,520 --> 01:01:35,120
he'll see the letter I wrote.

1476
01:01:35,120 --> 01:01:36,280
Do you think he'll like it?

1477
01:01:36,280 --> 01:01:38,600
I'm wondering
if there's durian-scented perfume.

1478
01:01:40,200 --> 01:01:41,000
That kind

1479
01:01:41,000 --> 01:01:43,480
of easy, in-sync vibe we share

1480
01:01:43,480 --> 01:01:45,840
is actually pretty rare.

1481
01:01:47,400 --> 01:01:48,480
If it's the right person,

1482
01:01:48,480 --> 01:01:49,680
whatever he says is fine.

1483
01:01:49,680 --> 01:01:50,680
Even if he says nothing.

1484
01:01:50,680 --> 01:01:51,160
Yeah.

1485
01:01:51,160 --> 01:01:52,720
After they confess, let's yell "kiss."

1486
01:01:52,720 --> 01:01:53,760
They kissed.

1487
01:01:53,760 --> 01:01:54,800
He's a pro.

1488
01:01:54,800 --> 01:01:55,640
Cheering them on.

1489
01:01:56,320 --> 01:01:58,160
(Watch Live and Love with us)
Hey everyone.

1490
01:01:58,160 --> 01:02:00,700
(On Thurs. at 12 pm.)
Today's our final episode.

1491
01:02:00,700 --> 01:02:01,600
(Confession Night)

1492
01:02:02,440 --> 01:02:03,320
What was I saying?

1493
01:02:03,420 --> 01:02:04,020
(I don't get myself.)

1494
01:02:04,100 --> 01:02:05,220
(Too honest)

1495
01:02:05,220 --> 01:02:06,380
I was seriously blunt.

1496
01:02:06,460 --> 01:02:07,140
(I just say what I think.)

1497
01:02:07,380 --> 01:02:09,140
(Rough words, but true.)

1498
01:02:10,150 --> 01:02:11,710
Oh my gosh.

1499
01:02:11,880 --> 01:02:12,360
So creepy.

1500
01:02:12,360 --> 01:02:13,800
I don't want to watch myself talking.

1501
01:02:13,980 --> 01:02:16,060
(You can't say that.)

1502
01:02:16,140 --> 01:02:17,260
(Help me out.)

1503
01:02:17,440 --> 01:02:18,080
I'm heading out.

1504
01:02:18,080 --> 01:02:19,240
(Can't bear to look.)

1505
01:02:19,240 --> 01:02:20,280
Can't sit still.

1506
01:02:21,010 --> 01:02:22,070
When's the kiss happening?

1507
01:02:23,160 --> 01:02:24,640
You kissed for two minutes, remember?

1508
01:02:24,640 --> 01:02:26,120
No way it was two minutes.

1509
01:02:26,280 --> 01:02:28,160
See? Still kissing.

1510
01:02:28,400 --> 01:02:29,720
Why is it this clip?

1511
01:02:29,720 --> 01:02:31,680
Looking forward to seeing you again.

1512
01:02:31,680 --> 01:02:32,880
Bye-bye.

1513
01:02:32,880 --> 01:02:34,000
Bye-bye.

1514
01:02:34,800 --> 01:02:36,080
(Balance Island Special Eventon Fri. 12 PM.)
Welcome to Balance Island.

1515
01:02:36,080 --> 01:02:38,560
Now it's islander game time.

1516
01:02:38,840 --> 01:02:39,480
(Can't lose)
Gotta win.

1517
01:02:39,520 --> 01:02:40,280
(Spare me)
Again?

1518
01:02:40,340 --> 01:02:40,820
(Be humble)

1519
01:02:40,900 --> 01:02:41,340
(Helpless)

1520
01:02:41,520 --> 01:02:42,720
(Button stuck)
It's so tricky.

1521
01:02:42,720 --> 01:02:43,520
That's it.

1522
01:02:43,520 --> 01:02:43,840
(Time's up)
We're good.

1523
01:02:43,840 --> 01:02:44,780
He's exhausted.

1524
01:02:44,840 --> 01:02:46,120
(Jealous)
Rock solid, Guanjie.

1525
01:02:46,440 --> 01:02:46,880
(Surprisingly smooth)
That was fast.

1526
01:02:47,720 --> 01:02:48,360
No points?

1527
01:02:48,360 --> 01:02:48,880
Zero points?

1528
01:02:49,040 --> 01:02:50,160
Seriously?

1529
01:02:50,240 --> 01:02:51,160
Hurry.

1530
01:02:51,560 --> 01:02:53,160
That's a sleeve.

1531
01:02:53,160 --> 01:02:54,000
(Complaining)
Not the collar.

1532
01:02:54,680 --> 01:02:55,680
Wrong hole.

1533
01:02:55,880 --> 01:02:57,840
(Still low down, legs shaking harder)
Stop shaking your legs.

1534
01:03:00,060 --> 01:03:00,660
(Totally fell apart)

1535
01:03:03,880 --> 01:03:04,520
Like this.

1536
01:03:04,920 --> 01:03:05,480
Yang.

1537
01:03:05,520 --> 01:03:06,460
You're a good match.

1538
01:03:06,600 --> 01:03:07,360
Really?

1539
01:03:07,440 --> 01:03:08,280
Really a good match.

1540
01:03:08,280 --> 01:03:08,920
How so?
